               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām (fols. 3ra-43vb)&#xD;
I-1) Introductory exhortation (fols. 3ra-4va)&#xD;
I-2) Taʾāmra Māryām: 30 miracles (fols. 4va-43vb)&#xD;
II) Discourse by John Chrysostom on the life and decollation of John the Baptist (fol. 44ra-60va) &#xD;
III) Homily on the finding of the head of John the Baptist (fols. 60vb-65ra)&#xD;
IV)  Homily by John Chrisostom on the glory of John the Baptist (65ra-74ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2; colophons 1-2.</summary>
